{"tid":302482,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙拿舊tweet激嬲利迷","createTime":"2017-06-29T12:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T12:12:56.000Z","uid":46892,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4407563979ddf5d851a60fab3021e2a7a95a10","tid":302482,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=wYcR8OGjEg2myXYcDAheuU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4bf09b2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】身為公眾人物，大部份都逃不過被網民起底和秋後算賬的命運，利物浦新兵穆罕默德沙拿就是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n穆罕默德沙拿（Mohamed Salah）剛以3900萬鎊從羅馬加盟利物浦，令一眾紅軍球迷歡天喜地，紛紛追蹤其社交網站，當其粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n有網民就發現沙拿去年7月曾於twitter，上載了一張自己和丹巴巴亞在車路士並肩作戰的相片，留言祝那時受重傷的前隊友早日康復。看到這張相片後，很多利迷都大表憤怒，更留言叫沙拿刪除這個post和相片。<br />\n<br />\n何解？原來這張相片拍自2014年4月27日車路士對利物浦的英超，利物浦在這場比賽因為謝拉特跣腳，被丹巴巴亞截得皮球後射入，最終落敗失卻英超冠軍。一眾紅軍球迷看到這相片，就回憶起這段慘痛歷史；未知在該仗正選上陣踢了60分鐘的沙拿，會不會「屈服」？"},{"pid":"4e6677be339e40c70f632ea97f680562092056b2","tid":302482,"uid":1289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"676e1fa3677a57914d95c50f0479abd6732e9a31","tid":302482,"uid":3342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"利狗真係難服侍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17eacf0351c73d0acb7db7c0192ee532c33c772","tid":302482,"uid":25916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"咁又係嬲D既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87f46a66a888e730e565cc2078c1d8016d2b145","tid":302482,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"得啦知啦"},{"pid":"922a5d582d143f38f3f8cd4ce6d73e47cff8973a","tid":302482,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}